messages.messageBody:
This is a heads-up for anyone else who may suffer the same fate,
and a thankful apology for anyone who's had to endure my whining
about my computer over the past few days. I found out tonight that
my computer is set up for Belguim. Now, for an American
company, shipping to England, I guess Belgium's not that far
away. Only a different language, currency, way of writing
numbers...

Anyway, thanks for listening and I hope the same fate never befalls
anyone else.
Tracy
